sources.description:
*Terror Trap* - While driving at night on a lonely road, the car of an estranged couple is hit twice by another car. A sheriff offers to take them to a motel. They are disturbed by noises from inside a room and soon realize that they're part of a sick and deadly game.
Stars: David James Elliott, Heather Marie Marsden, Michael Madsen, Jeff Fahey
